line_1: Thus noblest buildings are with ease effac'd,
line_2: And what's well wrote alone, will always last.

line_1: Their harmless joys disease too soon effac'd:
line_2: She found, with flagging wing subdued, oppress'd,
But when no more the room she grac'd,

line_1: Shall mourn the Fame of Jacob's Strength effac'd.
And all the horrors of the scene effac'd.
line_2: A flow'ry wreath her modest temples grac'd;
